title: Forest Hills Two Bedroom apartment
posting_body: ['Beautiful two bedroom, one bath available starting August 15 2022.', 'This apartment offers great walkability with public transit (MTA Subway F,E,R trains, LIRR, and many buses), restaurant, cafe, and shopping options all within blocks.', 'Additionally this apartment features an in-unit washer and dryer, full kitchen, bay window, fireplace all wrapped in a safe and quiet neighborhood.', 'Tentative open house date:', 'Coming soon!', 'Pets will be allowed on a case by case basis.', '(No loud/disturbing animals will be permitted)', 'What Should you expect during the application process?', 'All applicants will have their credit, criminal and tenant histories checked.', 'Move in costs will be first month’s rent plus an additional security deposit ($2499+2499= $5,000.00)', 'A $20 Background check fee will also be collected for every applicant.', 'Tenant will be responsible for electric utility bills.', 'Please respond to this ad with your name, phone number and a little about yourself.', 'Thank you for looking!', 'Video tour (please copy and paste the link into your browser):', 'https://youtu.be/ugKrBPHcriI']
